name: Puddler
description:
43-second video loop.
24 fps.
1920 x 1920
2020-2021
Puddler may be my only SFW artwork? Puddler is a refined, provocative video loop which would look fabulous displayed at any size but - the larger the better. This work was minted on Foundation, but will not be listed. Puddler will only be available for collection from Hic Et Nunc.
